OL,3,CTeenager drove tractor at police car
OL,4,Ccausing #10,000-worth of damage
OL,6,FA teenager has been jailed after
OL,7,Fdeliberately ramming a police car with
OL,8,Fa tractor - causing #10,000 worth of
OL,9,Fdamage.
OL,11,FAlfred Brereton appeared at Chester
OL,12,FCrown Court on Wednesday 1 May, were
OL,13,Fhe was sentenced to 30 months in
OL,14,Fprison.
OL,16,FThe 19-year-old, of Bickley Town Lane,
OL,17,FBickley, near Malpas in Cheshire, had
OL,18,Fearlier pleaded guilty to criminal
OL,19,Fdamage recklessly endangering life.
