OL,6,FOne of the officers told court how "he
OL,7,Fhad never been scared or fearful for
OL,8,Fmy life before this".
OL,10,FHe added: "The actions of the driver
OL,11,Fwere deliberate, we gave him no reason
OL,12,Fto use such a large and powerful
OL,13,Fagricultural vehicle against us, I
OL,14,Fbelieve he fully intended to hurt us."
OL,16,FPolice were called to reports of a
OL,17,Fsuspected drink driver in Malpas on 25
OL,18,FJuly 2024.
