OL,3,CTeenager drove tractor at police car
OL,4,Ccausing #10,000-worth of damage
OL,6,FThe caller reported that the man was
OL,7,Fdriving a tractor which had been
OL,8,Fparked outside a pub.
OL,10,FOfficers attended and shortly before
OL,11,Fmidnight they spotted a red tractor,
OL,12,Fdriven by Brereton, on a nearby road
OL,13,Fand activated the emergency equipment
OL,14,Fand ordered him to stop.
OL,16,FHowever, Brereton ignored the request
OL,17,Fand went off-road into a field.
