OL,3,CTeenager drove tractor at police car
OL,4,Ccausing #10,000-worth of damage
OL,6,FAs police followed the tractor,
OL,7,FBrereton reversed the vehicle before
OL,8,Fdeliberately ramming the police car,
OL,9,Fcausing more than #10,000 worth of
OL,10,Fdamage and leaving both officers
OL,11,Fshaken.
OL,13,FAs well as his custodial sentence,
OL,14,FBrereton was also banned from driving
OL,15,Ffor three years and three months,
OL,16,Fwhich will start upon his release from
OL,17,Fprison.
