OL,3,CTeenager drove tractor at police car
OL,4,Ccausing #10,000-worth of damage
OL,6,FDetective Constable Kelly Connolley,
OL,7,Fwho led the investigation, said: "I
OL,8,Fwelcome the sentence handed to
OL,9,FBrereton, which reflects the severity
OL,10,Fof his indefensible and extremely
OL,11,Fdangerous actions that day.
OL,13,F"He used an extremely powerful vehicle
OL,14,Fto deliberately ram the police car,
OL,15,Fwhich the aim of causing as much
OL,16,Fdamage as possible. It is only by
OL,17,Fchance that the two officers involved
OL,18,Fdid not sustain any serious injuries.
