OL,3,CTeenager drove tractor at police car
OL,4,Ccausing #10,000-worth of damage
OL,6,F"Brereton also caused more than
OL,7,F#10,000 to a response police car,
OL,8,Fleaving it off the road for several
OL,9,Fweeks while the car was repaired.
OL,11,F"He committed all of these actions
OL,12,Fknowing that had he just stopped for
OL,13,Fthe officers as requested, he would
OL,14,Fhave passed the drink drive test and
OL,15,Fbeen allowed to make his way home.
OL,17,F"Instead, he's now facing 30 months
OL,18,Fbehind bars, which will allow him to
OL,19,Freflect upon his actions."
